                <note rend="inline" type="source">811.51632 National City Bank/35: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Ambassador in Brazil</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Morgan</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1930-06-14T13:00:00-04:00"
                            >June 14, 1930—1 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>42. Your 33, June 11, 3 p.m., last paragraph. The Secretary spoke with Senhor
                    Freitas Valle this morning regarding the matter emphasizing the desirability of
                    a rapid settlement. Mr. Valle promised to cable to Rio regarding it.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Stimson</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
